__NAME__ purpose
specify macro to be executed automatically at the end of every page access
__END__


__NAME__ see also
Autoload, Preload
__END__

__NAME__ synopsis
<arg choice='plain'><replaceable>macro</replaceable></arg>
__END__


__NAME__ description
Specify an Interchange &glos-macro; to be invoked automatically, at the end of every
page access. This step is performed after all page parsing occurs,
just before the whole transaction ends.
</para><para>
In other respects, it behaves the same as its closely related
directive &conf-Autoload;.
__END__

__NAME__ notes
__END__
